author: @BrianArbuckle
text: Great videos!    FYI it looks like the "run_pipeline" will get the following error in Notebook: NameError: name 'run_pipeline' is not defined.  Quantopian recommends the follow when using Notebook:  from quantopian.pipeline import Pipeline from quantopian.pipeline import CustomFactor   from quantopian.research import run_pipeline   from quantopian.pipeline.data import morningstar   from quantopian.pipeline.data.builtin import USEquityPricing  Thank you so much for sharing!
